item.title: Aeromotive 11102 Pro-Series Fuel Pump
item.description:
Designed for crazy horsepower, its hard to find a more powerful, higher flowing, in-line fuel pump anywhere. Engineered for high-horsepower racing engines, this beautiful pump features our patent pending “dual chamber” pump design.
Fuel injected engines:
up to 2200 HP – naturally aspirated
up to 1700 HP – forced air induction
Carbureted engines:
Up to 2600 HP – naturally aspirated
Up to 2000 HP – forced air induction
• ORB-12 inlet and outlet ports.
• Beautifully plated with our electroless nickel process.
• Two ORB-12 AN-12 Male adapter fittings included.
• For EFI use regulator PN 13110, carbureted PN 13202 or PN 13212
• Perfect for “blow-through” carbureted engines up to 2000 HP.
• Fully submersible for custom, in-tank placement.
• Billet Speed Pump Controller (PN 16302) required for EFI street applications.

item.title: Aeromotive 11103 Tsunami EFI Fuel Pump
item.description: Tsunami EFI Fuel Pump

item.title: Aeromotive 11104 Eliminator-Series Fuel Pump
item.description:
This continuous duty “street warrior” supports big horsepower and maintains the drivability necessary for a true high performance street car. Designed for high horsepower streetstrip applications, EFI or Carbureted, it features our “dual chamber” pumping mechanism.
Fuel Injected Engines:
up to 1900 HP – naturally aspirated
up to 1400 HP – forced air induction
Carbureted Engines:
up to 2300 HP – naturally aspirated
up to 1700 HP – forced air induction
• ORB-12 inlet port and ORB-10 outlet port.
• For EFI applications use regulator PN 13110, carbureted PN 13212.
• Fully submersible for custom, in-tank placement.
• 25 more flow at pressure than our A1000 Fuel Pump.
• Perfect for “blow-through” carbureted engines up to 1700 HP.
• Billet Speed Pump Controller (PN 16306) required for EFI street applications.
